social_posts.post_text: Finished 3rd in the feature which locks us into the big show on Saturday. #dome #dirttrackracing #stlouis #gatewaydirtnationals

2nd at the Dome for the 2nd year in a Row. This race is one of a kind and it’s a must see in person type of event! 

Congratulations to my buddy @terbo_91 he drove a perfect race with the weight of the world on his shoulders. We are all family and when we lose someone it hurts us all.
The 2023 season is coming up fast….. are you ready?
2022 was another banner year!  Can’t wait to see what 2023 has is store.
Happy Birthday to my Beautiful wife and Super Mom to our Banks! We love you @mallorieelynn

Volusia bound in the AM….. Truck so clean!
#racing #dirtracing #dirtlatemodelracing #worldofoutlaws #sunshinestate #longhornchassis #trucksoclean
Night 1 at Volusia didn’t start how we had hoped. We ended up 13th in the feature after starting 24th. Now for night #2 at Volusia with the @woolatemodels.

Volusia hasn’t been kind to us.. we got into the wall in our primary car the first night and had to go to the backup car. Got up early yesterday and rebuilt the whole front end, only made 4 laps in it. Qualified 5th and the engine blew a front oil seal. So we had to switch to the other car and tag the tail of the heat race. Ended up 16th in the feature last night. We have a fast car just no luck.

📸: @heath_lawson
Ended Golden Isles with a 3rd place finish. Now we’re heading down south to Bubba with @lucasdirt!
Final night of speedweeks
We are racing at Clarksville, TN this weekend!
Two top 5’s at clarksville. Next stop Smokey Mountain with the @woolatemodels! If you weren’t able to pick up one of our new shirts this weekend they are now listed on the website!
Since mother nature is winning this weekend here’s a video from last weekend.

Next Destination….. Lucas Oil Speedway
